      <title>EXPERIMENTAL PROCEDURES</title>
      <p><italic>Antibodies and Reagents</italic>âAnti-human GPVI monoclonal antibody
 (mAb) 204-11 has been described previously
 (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref25">25</xref>). Anti-Syk polyclonal Ab
 (pAb) (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref26">26</xref>) was kindly provided
