 Î¼g/ml streptomycin, 50 Î¼<sc>m</sc> Î²-mercaptoethanol, and 20
 m<sc>m</sc> glutamine.</p>
      <p><italic>Luciferase Assay</italic>âThe NFAT reporter assay was performed as
 described (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref8">8</xref>,
 <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref24">24</xref>). The indicated amount of
 DNA of each construct and 15 Î¼g of NFAT-luciferase reporter construct were
 transfected by electroporation at 350 V and 500 microfarads into 2 Ã
 10<sup>7</sup> cells of WT, Syk-deficient, and SHP1/SHP2-deficient DT40 cells.
