 series of experiments were undertaken to investigate the possible regulation
 of constitutive and agonist-induced signaling through the GPVI-FcR
 Î³-chain complex and CLEC-2 by the platelet immunoglobulin receptor
 G6b-B, which contains two ITIMs in its cytosolic tail
