 S2). Expression of G6b-B also partially inhibited collagen-induced tyrosine
 phosphorylation of Syk (<xref rid="fig1" ref-type="fig">Fig.
 1<italic>C</italic></xref><italic>, panel ii</italic>), demonstrating a molecular basis
 for its inhibitory action. These results demonstrate that G6b-B inhibits
